      <h1>EU anti-subsidy probe becomes more absurd</h1>
      <h2></h2>
      <div class="info">
        <span class="info_l">
          By Chen Weihua | 
          China Daily |
          Updated: 2024-04-12 08:22
        </span>
        <span class="info_r">
          <a title="facebook" style="cursor:pointer; " target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?title=EU anti-subsidy probe becomes more absurd&amp;u=https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/a/202404/12/WS66187edda31082fc043c183c.html"><img src="https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/image_e/2020/facebook.png" height="17px" /></a>
          <a title="twitter" style="cursor:pointer;" target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/share?text=EU anti-subsidy probe becomes more absurd&amp;url=https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/a/202404/12/WS66187edda31082fc043c183c.html"><img src="https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/image_e/2020/twitter.png" /></a>
          <a title="linkedin" style="cursor:pointer;" target="_blank" href="http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;title=EU anti-subsidy probe becomes more absurd&amp;url=https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/a/202404/12/WS66187edda31082fc043c183c.html"><img src="https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/image_e/2020/linkedin.png" /></a>
